<div n="r" type="textpart"><ab>
    <lb n="1"/>Διονύσι<supplied reason="lost">ος</supplied> Τ<gap reason="lost" quantity="9" unit="character"/> <app type="editorial"><lem resp="PN W.B. Henry (from autopsy)">τ<supplied reason="lost">ῆι</supplied></lem><rdg><supplied reason="lost">τῇ</supplied></rdg></app> 

    <lb n="2"/><app type="editorial"><lem resp="PN C. Balamoshev (from image)"><unclear>ἀ</unclear>δελφῆι</lem><rdg><unclear>ἀ</unclear>δελφῇ</rdg></app> χ<unclear>αί</unclear>ρ<supplied reason="lost">ειν</supplied>, 

    <lb n="3"/>κόμισαι παρὰ τοῦ πατρὸς Χαι

    <lb n="4" break="no"/>ρήμονος <choice><reg>ἔσοπτρον</reg><orig>ὄσυπτρον</orig></choice> καὶ τὰ 

    <lb n="5"/>δελτάρια καὶ χιτῶνα 

    <lb n="6"/>Ταψόιτος. ἄσπασαι τὰ παιδία 

    <lb n="7"/>καὶ τοὺς ἐν οἴκωι, ἀσπάζεταί 

    <lb n="8"/>σε Χαιρήμων καὶ τὰ παιδία 

    <lb n="9"/>καὶ Ἄγαθός <unclear>σε</unclear> <unclear>ἀσπ</unclear>ά<unclear>ζεται</unclear> 

   <lb n="10"/>ἐρχομένῳ <app type="editorial"><lem resp="PN C. Balamoshev (from image)">σταφυλ<unclear>ὰς</unclear> <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character" precision="low"/></lem><rdg><unclear>στ</unclear><gap reason="illegible" quantity="3" unit="character"/><unclear>λ</unclear><gap reason="illegible" quantity="6" unit="character"/></rdg></app> 

   <lb n="11" rend="indent"/>ἐρρῶσθαί σε <expan>εὔχ<ex>ομαι</ex></expan> 

   <lb n="12"/>ἐπεὶ ὁ <expan>στρ<ex>ατηγός</ex></expan> μοι περὶ τού

   <lb n="13" break="no"/>του ἐπέθετο Ἀρίστων σοι 

   <lb n="14"/><choice><reg>ἀναγνώτω</reg><orig>ἀναγνώτο</orig></choice> τὸ πεμφθὲν αὐ

   <lb n="15" break="no"/>τῷ πιττάκιον. 

   <lb n="16" rend="indent"/><expan>ἐρρῶ<ex>σθαί</ex></expan> σε <expan>εὔχ<ex>ομαι</ex></expan>. 
</ab></div>
